  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Despite multiple credibility factors with achieved levels below required levels, the assurance level is declared High and the decision is Accepted — a compound overstatement inconsistent with the structural evidence. This package is synthetic adversarial data targeting COMPOUND-03.",
